  "The request records scope, estimate, schedule context, and access notes. Garment jobs continue into pickup and return delivery. Home and office jobs continue into scheduled on-site work and final completion checks.": "Arịrịọ a na-edekọ oke, atụmatụ, nhazi oge, na ndetu nnweta. Ọrụ uwe na-aga n'ihu n'ịkwalite na mbugharị. Ọrụ ụlọ na ụlọ ọrụ na-aga n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ n'ime saịtị na nlele ikpeazụ.",
