  "The workspace cleaning scope is actively in progress.": "Ogologo ihicha oghere ọrụ na-aga n'ihu.",
  "This does not skip booking review. It simply opens the payment path immediately so the team can confirm your payment faster.": "Nke a anaghị awụpụ nlebanya ntinye akwụkwọ. Ọ na-emepe ụzọ ịkwụ ụgwọ ozugbo ka ndị otu ahụ nwee ike kwado ịkwụ ụgwọ gị ngwa ngwa.",
  "This payment checkpoint stays tied to your Studio project, so payment status, proof visibility, and the next delivery step remain aligned.": "Ebe nlele ịkwụ ụgwọ a na-ejikọta na ọrụ Studio gị, yabụ ọkwa ịkwụ ụgwọ, ọhụhụ akaebe, na usoro nnyefe na-esote ga-adakọrịrị.",
  "This payment lane does not show an uploaded proof yet. If you already transferred, continue in the Studio project room or linked support room so the team can confirm the deposit cleanly.": "Ụzọ ịkwụ ụgwọ a egosighi akaebe ebugoro. Ọ bụrụ na ibufeelarị, gaa n'ihu n'ime ụlọ ọrụ Studio ma ọ bụ ọnụ ụlọ nkwado jikọtara ka ndị otu ahụ nwee ike kwado nkwụnye ego ahụ nke ọma.",
  "This service has been completed, so you can now share a verified review linked to your tracking code and booking phone number.": "Emechaala ọrụ a, yabụ ị nwere ike kesaa nyocha ekwenyesiri ike jikọtara ya na koodu nsochi yana nọmba ekwentị ntinye akwụkwọ.",
