  "Wardrobe care and return delivery": "Nlekọta wodrobu na nnyefe nnyefe",
  "Wardrobe care follows movement and delivery. Home and office cleaning follow on-site execution and completion quality. The timeline shown here matches the type of service you booked.": "Nlekọta akwa akwa na-esote mmegharị na nnyefe. Nhicha ụlọ na ụlọ ọrụ na-agbaso mmezu nke saịtị na ịdịmma mmecha. Usoro iheomume egosiri ebe a dabara ụdị ọrụ ị debere.",
  "Wardrobe requests are built around pickup, treatment, and return delivery. Home and office requests are built around team arrival, execution, inspection, and confirmed completion.": "A na-ewu arịrịọ Wardrobe gburugburu ntugharị, ọgwụgwọ, na nnyefe mbugharị. A na-ewu arịrịọ ụlọ na ụlọ ọrụ n'akụkụ mbata otu, mmezu, nleba anya na nkwenye na mmecha ya.",
  "Wardrobe service": "Ọrụ akwa akwa",
  "We keep your teaching application attached to the same HenryCo identity used across courses, certificates, and future academy operations.": "Anyị na-edobe ngwa nkuzi gị n'otu njirimara HenryCo nke a na-eji n'ofe ọmụmụ, asambodo, yana ọrụ agụmakwụkwọ n'ọdịnihu.",
  "We look for real subject expertise, respectful delivery, and outlines learners can actually finish—not hype or recycled slides.": "Anyị na-achọ ezigbo isiokwu nka nka, nnyefe nkwanye ugwu, na kọwapụta ndị mmụta nwere ike imecha ya—ọ bụghị ịgba egwu ma ọ bụ ihe mmịfe emegharịrị.",
  "We review every application by hand. Approval is not automatic. Strong candidates move through identity checks, quality expectations, and onboarding—not a self-serve creator rush.": "Anyị na-eji aka na-enyocha ngwa ọ bụla. Nkwenye abụghị akpaka. Ndị na-eme ntuli aka siri ike na-agafe na nyocha njirimara, atụmanya ịdị mma, na ịbanye n'ụgbọ mmiri-ọ bụghị ngwa ngwa onye okike na-ejere onwe ya ozi.",
  "We take instructor applications seriously.": "Anyị na-eji ngwa nkuzi kpọrọ ihe.",
  "We validate your identity against your HenryCo profile, read your credentials and samples, and assess whether your proposed course fits our learners and quality bar. Most applications receive a decision or a request for more detail—not instant approval.": "Anyị na-akwado njirimara gị megide profaịlụ HenryCo gị, gụọ nzere gị na ihe nlele gị, wee chọpụta ma usoro ọmụmụ gị dabara adaba na ndị na-amụ ihe na ụlọ mmanya dị mma. Ọtụtụ ngwa na-enweta mkpebi ma ọ bụ arịrịọ maka nkọwa ndị ọzọ - ọ bụghị nnabata ozugbo.",
  "We’re already reviewing this submission.": "Anyị enyochala nrubeisi a.",
  "We’re here when something blocks your learning.": "Anyị nọ ebe a mgbe ihe gbochiri mmụta gị.",
  "What “done” means": "Ihe “emere” pụtara",
