  "Volume customers with negotiated SLA + billing terms. Bulk shipment composer lives inside the customer-side B2B admin.": "Ndị ahịa nke nwere oke ego na SLA na usoro ịkwụ ụgwọ akwadoro. Onye nhazi nzipu nke ukwuu dị n'ime onye nchịkwa B2B ndị ahịa.",
  "Volume, on-time %, exceptions, revenue, and fleet utilisation. Click a metric for the per-corridor breakdown.": "Hà, pacenti n'oge, mwepu, ego mbata, na ojiji ụgbọ ala. Pịa nha ahụ maka nkewa kwa corridor.",
  "We could not find": "Anyị enweghị ike ịchọta",
  "We couldn’t find a shipment for that code and phone combination. Confirm the code on your booking confirmation and use the same phone you listed as sender or recipient. If both look correct, the dispatch desk can verify your record.": "Anyị enweghị ike ịhụ nzipu maka koodu na ekwentị ahụ. Kwadoro koodu na nkwado ndabere gị ma jiri otu ekwentị i depụtara dị ka onye zigara ma ọ bụ onye nnata. Ọ bụrụ na ha abụọ dị mma, ndị nzipu nwere ike ikwenye ndekọ gị.",
  "We never show internal dispatch noise — only the events both sides can act on.": "Anyị anaghị egosi ụzụ nzipu n'ime — naanị mmemme nke akụkụ abụọ niile nwere ike imeghari.",
  "We render the route as soon as either pickup or dropoff has a precise coordinate. Live rider breadcrumbs join automatically once dispatch shares the position.": "Anyị na-egosi ụzọ ozugbo iburu ma ọ bụ ihichapu nwere mkpọmkpọ ebe kpọmkwem. Akara onye ngwa dị ndụ na-akpara n'akpaghị aka ozugbo ndị nzipu kekọrọ ọnọdụ ahụ.",
