  "When a customer files a claim it appears here with their evidence and the shipment context.": "Mgbe onye ahịa boro mkpesa, ọ na-apụta ebe a tinyere ihe akaebe ya na nkọwa nzipu.",
  "When a shipment slips its SLA or fails a delivery attempt, it appears here with a recommended next action.": "Mgbe nzipu gafere SLA ya ma ọ bụ dara ọnwụnwa nnyefe, ọ na-apụta ebe a tinyere omume na-esote akwadoro.",
  "When dispatch assigns a leg or a customer asks a question, the alert lands at the top of this list with an audible toast on mobile.": "Mgbe ndị nzipu nyere akụkụ ma ọ bụ onye ahịa jụọ ajụjụ, ịdọ aka ná ntị na-apụta n'isi ndepụta a tinyere toast na-anụ ụda na mobile.",
  "When dispatch assigns a leg you'll see it here. Keep an ear on the alerts tab — assignments push there first.": "Mgbe ndị nzipu nyere gị akụkụ ị ga-ahụ ya ebe a. Lebe mkpado ịdọ aka ná ntị anya — nnyefe na-aga ebe ahụ buru ụzọ.",
