  "When do I get a certificate?": "Nigbawo ni MO gba ijẹrisi kan?",
  "Where a program is paid, HenryCo may offer revenue share or other instructor compensation. Terms are agreed in writing after approval—they are not promised on this page and vary by program. We never ask for payment to review your application.": "Nibiti a ti san eto kan, HenryCo le funni ni ipin owo-wiwọle tabi isanpada oluko miiran. Awọn ofin ti gba ni kikọ lẹhin ifọwọsi — wọn ko ṣe ileri ni oju-iwe yii ati yatọ nipasẹ eto. A ko beere fun sisanwo lati ṣe ayẹwo ohun elo rẹ.",
  "Where the project is right now": "Ibi ti ise agbese na wa ni bayi",
