  "This route is read-only. It only reflects subscription rows that a division has already written into `customer_subscriptions`.": "Ọ̀nà yìí jẹ́ fún kíkà nìkan. Ó ń fi àwọn ila ìforúkọsílẹ̀ hàn nìkan tí ẹ̀ka kan ti kọ sínú `customer_subscriptions` tẹ́lẹ̀.",
  "Management is still owned by the division workspace. The account hub can deep-link you there, but it does not mutate subscription state directly.": "Ìṣàkóso ṣì jẹ́ ti ibi iṣẹ́ ẹ̀ka náà. Ilé-iṣẹ́ àkọọlẹ lè darí ọ síbẹ̀, ṣùgbọ́n kò yí ipò ìforúkọsílẹ̀ padà taara.",
  "No direct management route has been published for this division inside the account hub yet, so there is no manage action to expose here.": "Kò tíì sí ọ̀nà ìṣàkóso taara tí a ti tẹ̀ jáde fún ẹ̀ka yìí nínú ilé-iṣẹ́ àkọọlẹ, nítorí náà kò sí ìṣe ìṣàkóso láti fi hàn níbí.",
  "Linked invoices and support threads below are shown only when the shared ledger uses one of this subscription's published reference keys.": "Àwọn ìnifòìsì àti àwọn okun atilẹyin tó wà ní isalẹ máa hàn nìkan nígbà tí ìwé àkọọlẹ apapọ̀ bá lo ọ̀kan lára àwọn bọtini ìtọ́kasí tí ìforúkọsílẹ̀ yìí ti tẹ̀ jáde.",
  "This subscription row has no published reference key beyond its own record, so invoice/support linkage depends entirely on future division-side sync quality.": "Ila ìforúkọsílẹ̀ yìí kò ní bọtini ìtọ́kasí tí a tẹ̀ jáde yàtọ̀ sí ìgbasilẹ tirẹ̀, nítorí náà ìsopọ̀ ìnifòìsì/atilẹyin dá lórí didara ìmúdọ̀gba ọjọ́ iwájú ti ẹ̀ka náà pátápátá.",
