  "The verified filter on the jobs board narrows to employers who have cleared review. If something looks off, the help page tells you exactly how to flag it.": "Àlẹ̀mọ́ tí a ti rí ìjẹ́rìí rẹ̀ lórí pátákó iṣẹ́ ń dín kù sí àwọn agbanisíṣẹ́ tí ó ti kọjá àyẹ̀wò. Bí nǹkan kan bá dàbí àjèjì, ojú-iwé ìrànlọ́wọ́ máa sọ fún ọ bí o ṣe lè fi sí àkíyèsí.",
