  "The request records scope, estimate, schedule context, and access notes. Garment jobs continue into pickup and return delivery. Home and office jobs continue into scheduled on-site work and final completion checks.": "Buƙatun yana yin rikodin iyaka, kimantawa, mahallin jadawalin, da bayanan shiga. Ayyukan tufafi suna ci gaba da ɗauka da dawowa. Ayyukan gida da ofisoshi suna ci gaba da zuwa aikin da aka tsara a kan rukunin yanar gizo da kuma duba kammalawar ƙarshe.",
  "The rider is moving the finished order back to the customer.": "Mahayin yana motsa odar da aka gama zuwa ga abokin ciniki.",
  "The service is actively being completed on site.": "Ana kammala sabis ɗin akan wurin.",
  "The service request has been received and opened for planning.": "An karɓi buƙatar sabis kuma an buɗe don tsarawa.",
  "The service slot is confirmed for the site.": "An tabbatar da ramin sabis don rukunin yanar gizon.",
