  "Want to teach?": "Kuna son koyarwa?",
  "Wardrobe care and return delivery": "Kula da wardrobe da dawowar bayarwa",
  "Wardrobe care follows movement and delivery. Home and office cleaning follow on-site execution and completion quality. The timeline shown here matches the type of service you booked.": "Kulawar tufafi yana biye da motsi da bayarwa. Tsabtace gida da ofis suna bin aiwatar da aikin kan layi da ingancin kammalawa. Jadawalin lokaci da aka nuna anan yayi daidai da nau'in sabis ɗin da kuka yi rajista.",
  "Wardrobe requests are built around pickup, treatment, and return delivery. Home and office requests are built around team arrival, execution, inspection, and confirmed completion.": "An gina buƙatun wardrobe a kusa da ɗauka, jiyya, da dawowar bayarwa. Buƙatun gida da ofis an gina su a kusa da isowar ƙungiyar, aiwatarwa, dubawa, da tabbatar da kammalawa.",
  "Wardrobe service": "Sabis na tufafi",
  "We keep your teaching application attached to the same HenryCo identity used across courses, certificates, and future academy operations.": "Muna adana aikace-aikacen koyarwarku zuwa ga ainihin HenryCo da aka yi amfani da su a cikin kwasa-kwasan kwasa-kwasan, takaddun shaida, da ayyukan makarantar gaba.",
  "We look for real subject expertise, respectful delivery, and outlines learners can actually finish—not hype or recycled slides.": "Muna neman ƙwararrun batutuwa na gaske, bayarwa na mutuntawa, da kuma fayyace ɗalibai za su iya gamawa a zahiri-ba zage-zage ko zane-zanen sake fa'ida ba.",
  "We review every application by hand. Approval is not automatic. Strong candidates move through identity checks, quality expectations, and onboarding—not a self-serve creator rush.": "Muna duba kowace aikace-aikacen da hannu. Amincewa ba ta atomatik bane. Ƙarfafan ƴan takara suna motsawa ta hanyar bincikar shaidar mutum, tsammanin inganci, da hawan jirgi-ba gaggawar mahalicci mai son kai ba.",
  "We take instructor applications seriously.": "Muna ɗaukar aikace-aikacen koyarwa da mahimmanci.",
  "We validate your identity against your HenryCo profile, read your credentials and samples, and assess whether your proposed course fits our learners and quality bar. Most applications receive a decision or a request for more detail—not instant approval.": "Mun tabbatar da ainihin ku akan bayanan martaba na HenryCo, karanta takaddun shaidarku da samfuran ku, kuma muna tantance ko kwas ɗin da kuka gabatar ya dace da ɗalibanmu da mashaya mai inganci. Yawancin aikace-aikacen suna karɓar shawara ko buƙatar ƙarin daki-daki-ba yarda da sauri ba.",
  "We’re already reviewing this submission.": "Mun riga mun sake nazarin wannan ƙaddamarwa.",
  "We’re here when something blocks your learning.": "Muna nan lokacin da wani abu ya toshe karatun ku.",
  "What “done” means": "Abin da \"an yi\" yana nufin",
  "What deserves your attention now": "Me ya cancanci kulawar ku a yanzu",
  "What fits your current signal": "Me ya dace da siginar ku na yanzu",
  "What happens after submission": "Me ke faruwa bayan sallama",
  "What happens after you click submit.": "Me zai faru bayan ka danna sallama.",
  "What HenryCo can already see": "Abin da HenryCo zai iya gani",
  "What the request captures": "Abin da bukatar ya kama",
  "What were you trying to do, what happened instead, and any error text you saw?": "Me kuke ƙoƙarin yi, me ya faru maimakon haka, da duk wani rubutun kuskure da kuka gani?",
  "When do I get a certificate?": "Yaushe zan sami satifiket?",
  "Where a program is paid, HenryCo may offer revenue share or other instructor compensation. Terms are agreed in writing after approval—they are not promised on this page and vary by program. We never ask for payment to review your application.": "Inda aka biya shirin, HenryCo na iya ba da rabon kudaden shiga ko wasu diyya na malami. An yarda da sharuɗɗan a rubuce bayan amincewa - ba a yi musu alkawari a wannan shafin ba kuma sun bambanta da shirin. Ba mu taɓa neman biyan kuɗi don duba aikace-aikacenku ba.",
  "Where the project is right now": "Inda aikin yake a yanzu",
