  "Yes. Assigned programs appear in your account under Learn → Assignments while you complete them in the usual learning room.": "Ee. Shirye-shiryen da aka sanyawa suna bayyana a cikin asusunku ƙarƙashin Koyi → Ayyuka yayin da kuke kammala su a ɗakin koyo da aka saba.",
  "You can paste it into tracking, support, or any payment follow-up.": "Kuna iya liƙa shi cikin bin diddigi, tallafi, ko kowane biyan biyan kuɗi.",
