  "This thread is closed. If your issue returns, open a new request so it can be triaged and tracked cleanly.": "An rufe wannan zare. Idan matsalarku ta dawo, buɗe sabuwar buƙata don a iya tantance ta da kuma bibiyarta a sarari.",
