  "The lanes your fleet is licensed to operate. Edit base fee, SLA, and urgency multipliers per zone.": "Hanyoyin da tasoshinka ke da lasisin yin aiki. Gyara kuɗin tushe, SLA, da masu ƙarawa na gaggawa kowane yanki.",
