  "This does not skip booking review. It simply opens the payment path immediately so the team can confirm your payment faster.": "这不会跳过预订审核。它只是立即打开付款路径，以便团队可以更快地确认您的付款。",
  "This payment checkpoint stays tied to your Studio project, so payment status, proof visibility, and the next delivery step remain aligned.": "此付款检查点与您的 Studio 项目保持联系，因此付款状态、证明可见性和下一步交付步骤保持一致。",
  "This payment lane does not show an uploaded proof yet. If you already transferred, continue in the Studio project room or linked support room so the team can confirm the deposit cleanly.": "此付款通道尚未显示上传的证明。如果您已经转移，请继续在 Studio 项目室或链接的支持室，以便团队可以干净地确认押金。",
  "This service has been completed, so you can now share a verified review linked to your tracking code and booking phone number.": "此服务已完成，因此您现在可以分享链接到您的跟踪代码和预订电话号码的经过验证的评论。",
