  "Wardrobe care and return delivery": "衣柜护理和退货送货",
  "Wardrobe care follows movement and delivery. Home and office cleaning follow on-site execution and completion quality. The timeline shown here matches the type of service you booked.": "衣柜护理随着搬家和分娩而进行。家庭和办公室清洁遵循现场执行和完成质量。此处显示的时间表与您预订的服务类型相符。",
  "Wardrobe requests are built around pickup, treatment, and return delivery. Home and office requests are built around team arrival, execution, inspection, and confirmed completion.": "衣柜请求围绕取货、处理和退货进行。家庭和办公室的请求是围绕团队到达、执行、检查和确认完成而制定的。",
  "Wardrobe service": "衣柜服务",
  "We keep your teaching application attached to the same HenryCo identity used across courses, certificates, and future academy operations.": "我们将您的教学申请附加到在课程、证书和未来学院运营中使用的相同 HenryCo 身份。",
  "We look for real subject expertise, respectful delivery, and outlines learners can actually finish—not hype or recycled slides.": "我们寻找真正的学科专业知识、尊重的表达以及学习者可以实际完成的大纲，而不是炒作或回收的幻灯片。",
  "We review every application by hand. Approval is not automatic. Strong candidates move through identity checks, quality expectations, and onboarding—not a self-serve creator rush.": "我们手工审核每一份申请。批准不是自动的。优秀的候选人会通过身份检查、质量期望和入职，而不是自助式的创作者匆忙。",
  "We take instructor applications seriously.": "我们认真对待讲师申请。",
  "We validate your identity against your HenryCo profile, read your credentials and samples, and assess whether your proposed course fits our learners and quality bar. Most applications receive a decision or a request for more detail—not instant approval.": "我们根据您的 HenryCo 个人资料验证您的身份，阅读您的证书和样本，并评估您提议的课程是否适合我们的学习者和质量标准。大多数申请都会收到决定或提供更多详细信息的请求，而不是立即批准。",
  "We’re already reviewing this submission.": "我们已经在审核此提交内容。",
  "We’re here when something blocks your learning.": "当您的学习遇到障碍时，我们会随时为您服务。",
  "What “done” means": "“完成”是什么意思",
  "What deserves your attention now": "现在什么值得你关注",
  "What fits your current signal": "什么适合您当前的信号",
