  "Management is still owned by the division workspace. The account hub can deep-link you there, but it does not mutate subscription state directly.": "管理仍归属于业务工作区。账户中心可以直接带你过去，但不会直接修改订阅状态。",
  "No direct management route has been published for this division inside the account hub yet, so there is no manage action to expose here.": "该业务单元尚未在账户中心发布直接管理路径，因此这里没有可展示的管理操作。",
  "Linked invoices and support threads below are shown only when the shared ledger uses one of this subscription's published reference keys.": "只有当共享账本使用了该订阅已发布的某个引用键时，下方的关联发票和支持线程才会显示。",
  "This subscription row has no published reference key beyond its own record, so invoice/support linkage depends entirely on future division-side sync quality.": "这条订阅记录除了自身记录外没有已发布的引用键，因此发票和支持关联完全取决于业务侧未来的同步质量。",
